reviewText: product is as advertised. smae as the  VHS tape only now I can watch it with my DVD player as I no longer have a VCR.
I enjoyed watching this DVD. It provided some various insights into Angel encounters, who they are and why they exist. Interesting and thought provoking!

This book help me see past the physical and look inside myself for answers..
I can see the beauty all around me and know there is someone is always watching over us.

I found this DVD to be the most helpful instrument to really connect with my own guardian angel, and open up to the beauty of the angelic realm of being. I watched it once through and did the 1st meditation, and lo and behold, for the first time I had a truly beautiful connection with my inner wise and humorous angel.  A lovely, lovely and empowering DVD.
